								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "I named the Parser \"BrokenCalculatorParser\", named the Scanner \"BrokenCalculatorScanner\", and put them in \"GtWikiBridge\".\n{{gtClass:BrokenCalculatorParser}}\n{{gtClass:BrokenCalculatorScanner}}\nI tried translating the instructions from the SmaCC Booklet, but what I have isn't working and I don't know enough to debug it yet."
